Document: Making trees  
Path: godot/tutorials/shaders/making_trees.rst  
Summary: A tutorial on creating trees and vegetation in Godot, focusing on visual quality rather than modeling techniques.  

Making trees  
This is a short tutorial on how to make trees and other types of vegetation from scratch. The aim is to not focus on the modeling techniques (there are plenty of tutorials about that), but how to make them look good in Godot.
---CHUNK---
Start with a tree  
I took this tree from SketchFab:  
https://sketchfab.com/models/ea5e6ed7f9d6445ba69589d503e8cebf  
and opened it in Blender.
