Path: godot/tutorials/shaders/making_trees.rst
Summary: Recommended advanced reading on shader techniques from GPU Gems3, focusing on Crysis's sway code implementation.

Improving the shader There are many more resources on how to do this that you can read. Now that you know the basics, a recommended read is the chapter from GPU Gems3 about how Crysis does this (focus mostly on the sway code, as many other techniques shown there are obsolete): https://developer.nvidia.com/gpugems/GPUGems3/gpugems3_ch16.html